txt.en: Within Valdhellir, the most vicious Wargs of Elderslade dwell in darkness surrounded by countless skulls and other grisly trophies.\n\nYour mission is to destroy collections of grisly trophies kept by the Wargs in Valdhellir.
The Wargs of Elderslade keep numerous skulls of the slain as grisly trophies in Valdhellir.
You have completed your mission.\n\nYou should talk to Hórin for your reward.

'I have a new mission for you, [placeholder].

'My scouts have returned from Valdhellir with troubling news. It appears these Wargs are more canny than we expected! In addition to devouring those unlucky enough to cross their paths, they also keep grisly trophies in the darkened passages of Valdhellir. It is an insult to the slain and I will not allow it to stand!

'You are to travel to Valdhellir and destroy these trophies at once! For the Zhélruka! For the Gabil'akkâ!'
Monsters in this mission will apply a corruption buff to nearby allies.
Your mission is to destroy collections of grisly trophies kept by the Wargs in Valdhellir.\n\nYou should talk to Hórin and travel to Valdhellir.
'It is done then? Good.\n\n'You have my thanks for destroying those terrible trophies, [placeholder].'
